<Link id="l01494" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1494"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// The pointer is located at offset 16 of the Prefixed Save Area (PSA).</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01495" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1495"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// It is stored as 31 bit pointer and will be zero-extended to 64 bit.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01496" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1496"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">int</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> &#42;StartToCVTOffset = </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">reinterpret&#95;cast&lt;</Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">int</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> &#42;</Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">&gt;</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal">(0x10);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01497" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1497"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Since its stored as a 31-bit pointer, get the 4 bytes from the start</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01498" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1498"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// of address.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01499" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1499"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">int</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> ReadValue = &#42;StartToCVTOffset;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01500" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1500"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Explicitly clear the high order bit.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01501" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1501"><Highlight kind="normal">  ReadValue = (ReadValue &amp; 0x7FFFFFFF);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01502" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1502"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">char</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> &#42;CVT = </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">reinterpret&#95;cast&lt;</Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">char</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> &#42;</Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">&gt;</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal">(ReadValue);</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01504" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1504"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// signless packed decimal.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01505" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1505"><Highlight kind="normal">  uint16&#95;t <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/amdgpu/vgprindexmode/#a9afd95476c40096a5898ba0f06370b3a">Id</a> = &#42;(uint16&#95;t &#42;)&amp;CVT&#91;-6&#93;;</Highlight></CodeLine>
